<p>Smapti.</p>
<p>You are apparently made of pure awesome.</p>
<p>Blackwood is singlehandedly my favorite character on the site, which is a pretty big achievement for a creature lacking even a single hand.</p>
<p>Have a well-deserved upvote, encouragement, an ego boost and another recommendation to do one of his Lordship's journals starring his adventures at sea to capture a <a href="/scp-879">whale-like monster</a> preying upon shipping.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Blackwood vs. pirates!</span></p>
<p>Also, is it wrong that I'm now imagining the foundation staff panicking and dying in the Class-XK Event while his Lordship oozes about, telepathically yelling at 682 and giggling as whatever happens when 447 comes into contact with dead bodies happens to it? Any how astonishingly silly this would be to watch?</p>

							</div>

								
					
